---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
class:STATISTICS

An object for all the acquired statistics to be accessed from.

private int totalWords = 0;
private int totalLines = 0;
private int blankLines = 0;
private double avgWpL = 0;
private double avgLL = 0;

public Statistics(){};	//default constructor

Methods:

+ int getTotalWords()	// # Words processed
+ int setTotalWords()

+ int getTotalLines()	// # Lines processed
+ int setTotalLines()

+ int getBlankLines()	// # Blank lines removed
+ int setBlankLines()

+ double getAvgWpL()	// Avg words per line
+ double setAvgWpL()

+ double getAvgLL()	// Avg line length	
+ double setAvgLL()